=========================================================
PEAK VOLTAGE METERS
=========================================================

To measure peak voltage:
- desired time constant > .01 secs    10M * C = .01secs     C = 1e-9 = 1nf

This measures 10KV
     -----------
               |
             Diode  V
               | 
               |--------
               |       |
               R       |      R = 10 M    = 1e7
               |       |      C = 15 nf   = 15e-9
               |       C
              METER    |      TimeConst = R * C = 15e-2  = .15 sec
               |       |
     -------------------


